---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service" 
  description="Terms of Service for The Brand Crew"
  canonicalURL="https://thebrandcrew.lat/terms"
>
  <main id="main-content" style="padding: 4rem clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 4rem); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--terracota); text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.7'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">← Back to home</a>
    
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--body-dim); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Last updated: July 1, 2026</p>

    <div style="background: var(--glass-bg); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">By accessing and using The Brand Crew website and services, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Services</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The Brand Crew provides web design, development, and hosting services. We reserve the right to modify or discontinue services at any time without notice.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>Payment for services is required as outlined in our pricing structure:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        <li>50% deposit required at project start</li>
        <li>50% balance due upon project delivery</li>
        <li>All prices are in Argentine Pesos (ARS)</li>
        <li>Payments are non-refundable once work has commenced</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Project Timeline</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Project timelines are estimates and may vary depending on project complexity, client feedback, and revision requests. We will make reasonable efforts to meet agreed-upon deadlines.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">5. Revisions</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our pricing includes multiple revision rounds. Additional revisions beyond the agreed scope may incur extra charges.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Upon full payment, you own the final website design and content. We retain the right to showcase the work in our portfolio unless otherwise agreed.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">7. Client Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>Clients must provide:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        <li>Timely feedback and approvals</li>
        <li>Required content and materials</li>
        <li>Access to necessary accounts and services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">8. Hosting and Maintenance</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Domain registration (2 years) and hosting are included in our pricing. After the initial period, renewal fees apply.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The Brand Crew is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">10. Termination</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Either party may terminate the agreement with written notice. Deposits and payments for completed work are non-refundable.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">11. Governing Law</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">These terms are governed by the laws of Argentina.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">12. Contact</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">For questions about these Terms, contact us at:</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
        Email: <a href="mailto:hello@thebrandcrew.lat" style="color: var(--terracota); text-decoration: underline;">hello@thebrandcrew.lat</a><br>
        WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/5491124063009" style="color: var(--terracota); text-decoration: underline;">+54 9 11 2406-3009</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
